{
  "stem": "24409.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That they should give us a few more days, because if they go back, there will be a big scandal about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the Germans wanted to [INAUDIBLE] quietly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So-- but the German embassy wasn't ready to do anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when they arrested me now, I gave this girl to hold the telegram [INAUDIBLE] the police.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The police were nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They permitted me to send the telegram.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I sent the telegram to the German embassy, to the [NON-ENGLISH] shipping company in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] excellent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Strongly-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Extension of stay for at least three or five days is recommended, or is necessary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was on the evening of the 24th, on the afternoon of the 24th.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "On the 24th of December.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was no-- I knew that there would be nobody there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And on the 25th, there would be nobody there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Anyhow, in the meanwhile, I sent a telegram to the people in [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Sulina, said arrangements have been made to prolong trip-- order from Vienna, and Vienna consulate as follows.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Signed, so and so name, consulate in-- or embassy in Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Somebody whom I knew [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the next morning, I took off, of course, as fast as I could, and I had no trouble getting into Italy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And from Italy into Switzerland back again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then I was back again in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And this was the day-- this one day saved the I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Maybe there was something else in play, because there were very capable people working on meeting in Sulina too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Yeah, I know, but the Turk wanted a guarantee that she will not be confiscated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And Eri Jabotinski, the son of Jabotinski, said, I'm going with the ship.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
